metadata.name: Avery #1
metadata.description: Avery is a warm, lovely and full of courage kid . Like Travel all over the world, whether it is forest, ocean or space! During the journey, Avery will meet all kinds of magical animals and adventures together! Lead you to find the heart full of curiosity about the unknown world.   Avery is the embodiment of our childhood memories. Same like you and me, Playful ,confident, and has no fear of the future!  Welcome to join the world of avery, dream and adventure together!
